/*===========================================================================

FUNCTION cmph_map_cm_network_sel_mode_pref_to_orig_mode

DESCRIPTION
  This function translates a network selection mode preference to a
  to SD Orig mode.

DEPENDENCIES
  none

RETURN VALUE
  The  SD Orig Mode.

SIDE EFFECTS
  none
===========================================================================*/
